# AUR helper (pacman wrapper for the AUR)
## Install & update
paru -S <pkg>	Install from repos or AUR
paru	Update all repo + AUR packages
paru -Sua	Update only AUR packages
## Search & info
paru -Ss <term>	Search repos + AUR
paru -Si <pkg>	Show package info
paru <term>	Interactive search + install menu
## Maintain
paru -Rns <pkg>	Remove pkg, deps, and config
paru -Sc	Clean caches
paru -Qua	List available AUR updates
